ported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAs one does not harvest thorns and grapes together, the wicked will not be in the position of the righteous. There are two paths, so whichever path you take will bring you to its outcome.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/07\/27\/forgot-salawat-ala-nabi\/","url_meta":{"origin":32548,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Forgetting to send blessings on the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever forgets to send blessings upon me, he has missed the path to Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 908 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14031,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/06\/ibn-al-qayyim-sharia-justice\/","url_meta":{"origin":32548,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Qayyim on Sharia: Justice is the objective of law in Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim said, \u201cAllah Almighty has made clear by many of His laws that the purpose is to establish justice between His servants and for people to behave fairly. Whichever path leads to justice and fairness is part of the religion and does not contradict it.\u201d Source: al-\u1e6curuq al-H\u0323ikm\u012bya 1\/13\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/09\/nothing-in-jihad-but-qital\/","url_meta":{"origin":32548,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Nothing in the path of Allah but fighting?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: We were sitting with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when a young man approached us. When we saw him, we said, \u201cIf only this young man had given his youth and effort and strength in the path of Allah!\u201d The Prophet heard\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17374,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/28\/do-not-wish-for-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":32548,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Mawt: Do not wish for death, you might repent","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2013","form